10.3.7.3 Paccayānulomapaccanīya
Mahantaraduka
Cetasikaduka
Pañhāvāra
Paccayānulomapaccanīya
142.
2667Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe tīṇi, naadhipatiyā tīṇi, naanantare tīṇi, nasamanantare tīṇi, naaññamaññe ekaṃ, naupanissaye tīṇi (sabbattha tīṇi), namagge tīṇi, nasampayutte ekaṃ, navippayutte tīṇi, nonatthiyā tīṇi, novigate tīṇi.
